{"tid":2183032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果光復香港成功，你哋會唔會清算班藍絲同警察？","createTime":"2020-08-31T16:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T14:16:57.000Z","uid":282619,"like":169,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"113f1493a21770abdbe407ae0c820d9c59584b20","tid":2183032,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"我一定會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你啲藍絲講嘢無人性，大肚婆被推倒，仲要話祝小產，咁無性既人，我哋唔需要佢哋！<br />\n唔清算，日後只會禍患無窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人話，你咁做，同共產黨有咩分別？分別既係共產黨係為咗自己政權唔會比人推翻，而我哋咁做係希望一啲熱愛自由既人不被呢啲藍絲柒頭同化，不被中國化，正係清一次，之後就回復正常，變返自由城市<br />\n清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50480c4e767296abfef8f52fd283e7daa9e377b2","tid":2183032,"uid":282619,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"清算方法<br />\n打把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐吓監算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者其他方法？"},{"pid":"9c37e55eec06562aa8f21e25dead75d4f85c5cd3","tid":2183032,"uid":285763,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"斷頭台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e8e84bb96484f37113e02fbf3e5532bc3ee6a7","tid":2183032,"uid":24457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"監倉邊有咁多位"},{"pid":"03b165da34def135a81441f2f433ee1c20e742d3","tid":2183032,"uid":267680,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"全部強制送上大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5e1c06f667c7a7f24a678228b77bd87ebcde31","tid":2183032